|boxstyle_5=background-color: #9fe;
|1= 1. '''Prince Anahobe'''
|2= 2. [[Oanenokimi]] 
|3= 3. [[Emperor Kinmei]]
|6= 6. [[Emperor Keitai]]
|7= 7. [[Princess Tashiraka]] 
|12=12. Hikoushi no Ōkimi
|13=13. Furihime
|14=14. [[Emperor Ninken]]
|15=15. [[Princess Kasuga no Ōiratsume]] 
}}
